schools.name: Early College High School At Midland Colle

data.description: Beautiful corner lot in highly sought after neighborhood, 3 bedroom 2 bath, large open concept living, beautiful combination wood or gas fireplace, gorgeous windows with amazing natural light, every bedroom has walk in closet and built ins. Backyard is perfect for entertaining with a beautiful covered pergola and patio with lots of space for children and pets to run an play.  Bonus 20ft x 12ft storage building in back yard.  Wood privacy fence is in great shape.  Roof was replaced Sept 22 2023.
